            "video": "",
            "video_button_color": "primary",
            "title": "Wooden Fences",
            "desc": "<p>Wood fences are customizable, every wood fence we install is custom-built at your home. This allows us to tailor the fence to your home’s needs. A wood fence is a renewable resource. As a natural material, wood is a sustainable choice, especially when sourced responsibly. Wood’s natural properties help in dampening and reducing ambient noise. We install Western Red Cedar and Michigan White Cedar.</p><p>Benefits of Wooden Fences</p><ul><li>Exceptional Resilience</li><li>Local Sustainability</li><li>Low Maintenance</li><li>Time and Cost Savings</li><li>Versatile Application</li><li>Enhanced Property Aesthetics</li></ul>",
            "horizontal_align": "left",
            "link_title": "BROWSE Wooden Fences",
            "link": "shopify://collections/wood-fences",
            "bg_color_block": "rgba(0,0,0,0)",
            "bg_color_content": "#ffffff",
            "color_text": "#212121",
            "text_heading_color": false,
            "text_border_color": true
