        "image_exKRrc": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Black_Chainlink.jpg",
            "video": "",
            "video_button_color": "primary",
            "title": "Chain Link Fences",
            "desc": "<p>Chain link fences are a practical and cost-effective choice for homeowners, businesses, and property owners seeking a durable and versatile fencing solution. These fences are constructed using interwoven metal wires, typically made of galvanized steel, providing a range of benefits that make them a popular option for a wide variety of applications.<br/><br/>In addition to their durability, chain link fences are incredibly versatile. They come in various heights and can be customized to fit the specific needs of your property, whether you’re looking for a low-profile boundary fence or a taller security barrier. You can also choose from different gauges of wire to balance security with visibility, making them suitable for both residential and commercial settings.</p>",
            "horizontal_align": "left",
            "link_title": "BROWSE CHAINLINK FENCES",
            "link": "shopify://collections/chainlink-fence",
            "bg_color_block": "rgba(0,0,0,0)",
            "bg_color_content": "#ffffff",
            "color_text": "#212121",
            "text_heading_color": false,
            "text_border_color": true
