            "video": "",
            "video_button_color": "primary",
            "title": "Composite Fencing",
            "desc": "<p>Fenceworks works with Greenwood Fence for all of our composite installs. Greenwood is a distributor of high-quality modern European style fencing for the residential, commercial, industrial, and agricultural sectors. Greenwood fences combine aesthetics with durability that requires very little maintenance.</p><p>Benefits of composite fences:<br/>• Durability<br/>• Low maintenance<br/>• Strong Aluminum Posts<br/>• Premium Rails<br/>• Premium Composite Panels</p>",
