            "desc": "<p>PVC vinyl fences are a modern and practical choice for homeowners and property owners seeking a low-maintenance and versatile fencing solution. These fences are meticulously crafted from durable PVC (Polyvinyl Chloride) material, offering a host of advantages that make them a popular option for various outdoor applications.</p><p>Benefits of PVC / Vinyl Fencing:<br/>• Sleek and Contemporary<br/>• Exceptional Durability<br/>• Weather Resistance<br/>• Quick Installation<br/>• UV Protection</p>",
