            "title": "{{ article.title }} by Fenceworks ",
            "desc": "<p>When you buy from Fenceworks you are buying more than a fence, you are buying a promise. A Fenceworks’ fence offers you beauty, privacy and home security. Fenceworks, since 1967, is Chicagoland’s #1 choice for quality fences and professional installation. Fenceworks offers the widest selection of fence materials and fence styles, including Wood Fences, Chainlink Fences, Aluminum Fences, Composite Fences, PVC/Vinyl Fences. Our Western Red Cedar Fence is a Fenceworks’ specialty and one of our most popular Fence choices. Cedar Fences look great, age beautifully, and withstand the Chicago seasons year after year.</p>",
